<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a8Sep1932"><font color="red">8 September 1932</font> <i>NLPK</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to J. Ralph Pinker): In the last Sunday Express (4 September 1932) you must have seen a great publicity article about Miss Sara Allgood &hellip; take the necessary steps in case she thinks it unnecessary to apply to you before giving her evenings. </div>
